It is still difficult to pay for cold fine
In the early days of May, Mr. N.M.Ch (driver of T.N company in District 1, Ho Chi Minh City) brought the company's pickup truck to the registration, the report was still reported to 7 untreated violations. In which, 1 speed error is from 10 - 20 km/h on Ho Chi Minh City - Long Thanh - Dau Giay highway and other errors in Ninh Thuan, Ho Chi Minh City from March 2021. Worth mentioning, the process of paid for fines takes time to wait.
